OL,3,CCemetery closes its gates as
OL,4,C'disrespectful' parking damages graves
OL,6,FA cemetery in Bath has closed its
OL,7,Fgates permanently after people kept
OL,8,Fusing the site to park all day.
OL,10,FOne vehicle even crashed into a
OL,11,Fmemorial at Locksbrook Cemetery,
OL,12,Fcausing it to break up and collapse
OL,13,Fonto another gravestone.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for the site said an
OL,16,F"increasing" number of people have
OL,17,Fbeen parking at the cemetery for hours
OL,18,Fat a time or even leaving their
OL,19,Fvehicles there all day.
