OL,3,CCemetery closes its gates as
OL,4,C'disrespectful' parking damages graves
OL,6,F"Misuse of the site is disrespectful
OL,7,Fto those laid to rest, and to those
OL,8,Fvisiting graves," they added.
OL,10,F"In the last week our worst fears were
OL,11,Frealised when memorials were damaged
OL,12,Fby a vehicle."
OL,14,FAs a result, Bath and North East
OL,15,FSomerset Council - which runs the site
OL,16,F- says it has made the "difficult"
OL,17,Fdecision to permanently close the main
OL,18,Fgates to prevent further damage.
