OL,3,CCemetery closes its gates as
OL,4,C'disrespectful' parking damages graves
OL,6,FPedestrian access is still available,
OL,7,Fand there are a few parking spaces
OL,8,Foutside the gates for legitimate
OL,9,Fcemetery visitors.
OL,11,FA council spokesperson said: "We
OL,12,Fprovide parking spaces at Locksbrook
OL,13,FCemetery for our visitors directly
OL,14,Foutside the front gates so it remains
OL,15,Faccessible, however in recent months
OL,16,Fwe have seen a significant number of
OL,17,Fvehicles parked for several hours and
OL,18,Fmany for the whole day whose drivers
OL,19,Fdo not appear to be visiting the
OL,20,Fcemetery.
