OL,3,CCemetery closes its gates as
OL,4,C'disrespectful' parking damages graves
OL,6,F"Last week a vehicle collided with one
OL,7,Fof the memorials, causing it to break
OL,8,Fup and collapse onto another
OL,9,Fgravestone.
OL,11,F"This is wholly unacceptable and
OL,12,Fdisrespectful to people's loved-ones.
OL,14,F"We have taken the difficult decision
OL,15,Fto permanently close the main gates to
OL,16,Fprevent further damage as it is
OL,17,Fimpossible to monitor vehicles within
OL,18,Fthe cemetery.
